OL,3,CStarmer divorces from Trump over the
OL,4,CIran war
OL,6,F"This government does not believe in
OL,7,Fregime change from the skies." So said
OL,8,Fthe PM to the "father of the House of
OL,9,FCommons", the Tory MP Sir Edward
OL,10,FLeigh, about why UK jets are not
OL,11,Fbombing Iran.
OL,13,FThis was the prime minister declaring
OL,14,Findependence from the US President
OL,15,FDonald Trump. It was a big moment.
OL,17,FStarmer made two significant points to
OL,18,FMPs this afternoon.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@^O]pD@OOUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772489474
OL,3,CStarmer divorces from Trump over the
OL,4,CIran war
OL,6,FFirst that Trump's and Netanyahu's war
OL,7,Fon Iran is illegal, so he was sure the
OL,8,FUK could not and would not participate
OL,9,Fin it.
OL,11,FSecond he made clear that Trump has no
OL,12,Fplan to bring peace and stability to
OL,13,FIran, as and when the war ends, and
OL,14,Fthis was a second reason why the UK
OL,15,Fcould not join offensive action
OL,16,Fagainst Iran. In arguing this case, he
OL,17,Fmade explicit reference to the debacle
OL,18,Fin Iraq after the US and UK invasion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
