PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772489474
OL,3,CStarmer divorces from Trump over the
OL,4,CIran war
OL,6,FAll of this is a point of significant
OL,7,Ftension between Starmer and the leader
OL,8,Fof the opposition Kemi Badenoch. She
OL,9,Fargues Tehran is such a threat to
OL,10,FMiddle East and global security that
OL,11,FStarmer should have given more
OL,12,Fexplicit support to Trump and Israel,
OL,13,Fincluding putting UK military bases at
OL,14,Fthe disposal of US bombers from the
OL,15,Foutset.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
