FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772489474
OL,3,CStarmer divorces from Trump over the
OL,4,CIran war
OL,6,FFor what it's worth, the PM has much
OL,7,Fof the House of Commons on his side
OL,8,Fbut a significant proportion of the
OL,9,FUK's security and military
OL,10,Festablishment against him.
OL,12,FThere is a critique of Starmer, that I
OL,13,Fhave heard from soldiers and spies,
OL,14,Fthat the British national interest
OL,15,Fshould be less about following
OL,16,Finternational law and more about a
OL,17,Fhard-nosed assessment of how to keep
OL,18,Fthe country safe and secure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
