FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772489474
OL,3,CStarmer divorces from Trump over the
OL,4,CIran war
OL,6,FThis war is dividing parliament, the
OL,7,Fmilitary and the country. It has also,
OL,8,Ffor the first time, seen Starmer
OL,9,Fsiding very explicitly with France's
OL,10,FMacron and Germany's Merz and
OL,11,Fdistancing himself also explicitly
OL,12,Ffrom the American president.
OL,14,FThe consequences of choosing Europe
OL,15,Fover Trump and America will go well
OL,16,Fbeyond this war, hugely important as
OL,17,Fthat war is.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
